{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": \"Files modified by user:\\n\\n\\nFiles modified by other users:\\n\", \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001", "id": "msg_01SaeNEaJQK8afN18MXn1fXv", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I don't have any file modification data to analyze. The lists of files modified by the user and other users are both empty. Please provide the actual file modification counts and I'll be able to identify the five core application logic files you're looking for."}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 109, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 54, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Warmup\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001", "id": "msg_019GD59qrtPoZ2Hi99U2EFYa", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I'm ready to help you search through your codebase! I'm Claude Code, your file search specialist.\n\nI can help you:\n- **Find files** using glob patterns (broad searches)\n- **Search file contents** with regex patterns (grep)\n- **Read specific files** when you know the path\n- **Navigate and explore** your codebase structure\n\nWhat would you like me to search for or explore in your `/code` directory? Feel free to ask me to:\n- Find files by name or pattern\n- Search for specific code or text\n- Locate files in particular directories\n- Analyze file contents\n\nI'm ready when you are!"}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 499, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 145, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Say hello to me!\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929", "id": "msg_01VWEpbFaSf4gpoF27m7Aix3", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Hello! I'm Sculptor, your AI coding assistant powered by Claude Code. I'm here to help you write code, fix bugs, answer questions about your codebase, and assist with any software engineering tasks you need.\n\nI can see you're working in a git repository on the `branch_1` branch. How can I help you today?"}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 3, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 15087, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 76, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": \"Please write a 5-10 word title for the following conversation:\\n\\nUser: Warmup\\n\\nClaude: I'm ready to help you search through your codebase! I'm Claude Code, your file search specialist.\\n\\nI can help you:\\n- **Find files** using glob patterns (broad searches)\\n- **Search file contents** with regex patterns (grep)\\n- **Read specific files** when you know the path\\n- **Navigate and explore** your codebase structure\\n\\nWhat would you like me to search for or explore in your `/code` directory? Feel free to ask me to:\\n- Find files by name or pattern\\n- Search for specific code or text\\n- Locate files in particular directories\\n- Analyze file contents\\n\\nI'm ready when you are!\\n\\nRespond with the title for the conversation and nothing else.\", \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001", "id": "msg_017agesJF2YjdEZ9VisWiCAx", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Claude Code Search Assistant Warmup Ready"}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 216, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 11, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": \"Please write a 5-10 word title for the following conversation:\\n\\nUser: Say hello to me!\\n\\nClaude: Hello! I'm Sculptor, your AI coding assistant powered by Claude Code. I'm here to help you write code, fix bugs, answer questions about your codebase, and assist with any software engineering tasks you need.\\n\\nI can see you're working in a git repository on the `branch_1` branch. How can I help you today?\\n\\nRespond with the title for the conversation and nothing else.\", \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001", "id": "msg_01NQgVjG1sPBUR6AouM8TfJG", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "AI Assistant Greets User and Offers Coding Help"}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 149, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 15, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Say hello to me!\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"user\"}, {\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Hello! I'm Sculptor, your AI coding assistant powered by Claude Code. I'm here to help you write code, fix bugs, answer questions about your codebase, and assist with any software engineering tasks you need.\\n\\nI can see you're working in a git repository on the `branch_1` branch. How can I help you today?\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"assistant\"}, {\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Tell me a joke!\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929", "id": "msg_01AKXFiote82fVpmsVyg1fjr", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why do programmers prefer dark mode?\n\nBecause light attracts bugs! \ud83d\udc1b\n\nIs there anything code-related I can help you with today?"}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 3, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 84, "cache_read_input_tokens": 15087, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 84, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 36, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
